-照顧子女積勞成疾<br />\n51-60歲打完死-感冒長期病患<br />\n60-70歲打完死-糖尿病長期病患<br />\n71-80歲打完死-高血壓長期病患<br />\n80+打完死-任何長期病患"},{"pid":"a0fdae041c0b1bfe98bfeaa0fe76ea0acaa97103","tid":2430381,"uid":357308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:01:18.000Z","msg":"許樹昌一陣會出黎話死者死時63歲，打個時未滿60歲。"},{"pid":"c568d5cb94d77950ad91bbb1b52fab133ecc0be6","tid":2430381,"uid":76133,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:02:55.000Z","msg":"科興正正是缺乏第三期臨床數據，第三期測試對象正是年滿60歲或長期病患者. <br />\n港共提供長者係為科興完成第三期臨床數據"},{"pid":"71b80e7317f72912691db73c23e653b63d9f8cb9","tid":2430381,"uid":17443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:03:06.000Z","msg":"唔跟指引，自己報名接種，今次唔駛賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a175dbedf0aa9b8a6881367b5f19f99fbdfe75","tid":2430381,"uid":5475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:07:04.000Z","msg":"第三同第七點 糖尿都中晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e4b46e319d59f6dab76280a6292170d89e0663","tid":2430381,"uid":174013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T02:07:25.000Z","msg":"之前就話要保住依班廢老鐵票姐<br />\n而家有新玩法<br />\n唔比入閘又得，當選後dq又得，喺支那投票又得,根本贏撚硬<br />\n政府仲洗撚保住班對社會零貢獻既廢老咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n恨不得快快手清除晒tim"},{"pid":"8cdf553f37ec92f5d5ffae1c43be5974a195232d","tid":2430381,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e0081f5624c9ee4c7cc5bd60ea03407c73beb4d7","tid":2430381,"uid":5993,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"fb7a32823ca74c76245a9d4fce524927ce7e376e","tid":2430381,"uid":262224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T01:48:08.000Z","msg":"香港就理得你 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AU